{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvDecideGoal\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbvDecideGoal</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Attempt to close a goal of the form `decide P = true` by reducing only the LHS using `cbv`.\n\n- If the LHS reduces to `Bool.true`, the goal is closed successfully.\n- If the LHS reduces to `Bool.false`, throws a user-friendly error indicating the proposition is false.\n- Otherwise, throws a user-friendly error showing where the reduction got stuck.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvDecideGoal","kind":"def","line":426,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvDecideGoal","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.lean#L426-L454"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoal\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbvGoal</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">mvarId</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">simplifyTarget</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.true\">true</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">fvarIdsToSimp</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.FVarId\">FVarId</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.toArray\">#[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.toArray\">]</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reduce goal target and/or hypothesis types using call-by-value evaluation.\n\nPreprocesses the goal via `Sym.preprocessMVar` (instantiates metavariables, unfolds\nreducibles, shares common subterms), then runs `cbvCore` on each selected hypothesis\nand the target within a single `SymM` context.\n\nFor each hypothesis in `fvarIdsToSimp`, reduces its type via `cbvCore`. If the\nreduced type is `False`, the goal is closed immediately. Otherwise, the hypothesis\nis replaced with the reduced type.\n\nIf `simplifyTarget` is true, reduces the goal type via `cbvCore`. If the reduced\ntype is `True`, the goal is closed. Otherwise, the target is replaced.\n\nAfter all reductions, attempts `refl` to close equation goals of the form `v = v`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoal","kind":"def","line":406,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoal","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.lean#L406-L424"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoalCore\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbvGoalCore</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">mvarId</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">simplifyTarget</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.true\">true</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">fvarIdsToSimp</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.FVarId\">FVarId</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.toArray\">#[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.toArray\">]</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">Sym.SymM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Core of `cbvGoal`: reduces the selected hypotheses and/or target of an already\npreprocessed `mvarId` using call-by-value evaluation, within the caller's `SymM` context.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoalCore","kind":"def","line":350,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoalCore","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.lean#L350-L404"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvEntry\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbvEntry</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/SimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Result\">Sym.Simp.Result</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reduce a single expression. Unfolds reducibles, shares subterms, then runs the\nsimplifier with `cbvPre`/`cbvPost`. Used by `conv => cbv`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvEntry","kind":"def","line":333,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvEntry","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.lean#L333-L348"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbv.maxSteps\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">maxSteps</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbv.maxSteps","kind":"opaque","line":108,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbv.maxSteps","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.lean#L108-L111"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbv.warning\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">warning</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbv.warning","kind":"opaque","line":103,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbv.warning","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.lean#L103-L106"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Sym","Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.SimpM","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Assert","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.BuiltinCbvSimprocs.Array","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.BuiltinCbvSimprocs.Core","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.BuiltinCbvSimprocs.String","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvEvalExt","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimproc","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.ControlFlow","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.Opaque","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.TheoremsLookup","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.Util","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Refl","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Replace"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.Main"}